Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your ridiculous attacks wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:03:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but die in that stupid state, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol! Spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to normal, body!\NHurry! Hurry! I'm gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damage I took earlier is affecting my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm going back...!\NI'm going back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? My attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did a number on you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something...! Or we'll all drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we still haven't really\Ngotten Robin-chan back yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...! Everything's going dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine. Get ahold of yourselves!\NI'm not gonna let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is being pulled by something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several sailors are drowning in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As their consciousness fades away,\Nthey see an elegant tail fin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they look up, they see\Nlong hair swaying in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mermaid legend...\NIt's like we're seeing a fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm dreaming... please don't let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go super express!\NMake sure you hold your breath tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Du...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Du...\N--Du...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Du... A dugong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cannon Fire Sinks the Island!\NFranky's Lamentation"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:06:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, marines! We're gonna\Nuse this ship to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we've finished cleaning out our\Nescape ship, the former escort ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do now is wait\Nfor Straw Hat and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships 6, 7, and 8 identified\Npirates in front of the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can only be described as a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've... They must've\Nreceived a tremendous shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all stopped breathing,\Nso they didn't swallow much water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing they're all okay... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what on earth could have shocked them\Nenough to make them stop breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the friend that\Npirate king kid came to rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you at the Shift\NStation, right? I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I never thought that you guys\Nwould pull something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put some clothes on, you damn old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed when I heard him say he\Nwas gonna be King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but who knows? It might actually happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nami-san okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are as tough as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! So it was real!\NMermaids really don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the tales were true about\Npeople seeing a mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then realizing it was actually a dugong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You morons! She still hasn't\Nsaid she's a mermaid yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on the dream yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an icefish mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't say "icefish"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never heard of a mermaid with legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an objection, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaids should be more...\NMermaids should be more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A well-proportioned sexy body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth white skin and flowing hair\Nthat's beaming and beautiful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When mermaids are around 30,\Ntheir tail fins fork into two
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they become able to live on land.\NThey're a mysterious species.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to the Fishman\NIsland one day, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Fork into two...? Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say when a cat lives 100 years, its tail\Nsplits into two and it becomes a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a goblin cat, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me in with monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least say\Nthank you for what I did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Kokoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we made it in time,\NRobin! So you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! That's amazing!\NSo you were a mermaid all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking you were different,\Nsince you have fins and scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've noticed, grandkid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising. We'll tell you\Nwhat happened when this is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! I mean, Zoro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that's the island\Nwe were on up until just a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this attack?\NIt's already a sea of flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they've been ordered\Nnot to kill Nico Robin in their attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why this bridge\Nisn't being targeted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their trying not to kill her must mean\Nthey still intend to get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After completely destroying Enies Lobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll probably engage in some\Nclose combat to get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, isn't that bad?\NWe're all physically wrecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, there are lots of crazy\Npowerful guys on those battleships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the dust of combat still coming up\Nfrom the top of this bridge's first column.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent is, of course,\Nthat pigeon guy, Rob Lucci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not far from here! If we give him a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pigeon guy is no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if we get dragged\Ninto the fight and get separated again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure we still have an escape route
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of when that group\Nof battleships turns this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll wait for Luffy right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all we need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storm is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your legs are being affected after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Looks like your ridiculous way\Nof fighting isn't just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't underestimate the inner\Nstrength of a Six Powers Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to master the ultimate techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you need the ultimate inner strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick! Victory Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... your guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn idiot!\NThey've got the luck of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fine. I'm sure they've escaped okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Paulie! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're picking up a transponder snail?!\NWhat're you gonna do with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can find out how the Straw Hats are doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It's a cannon attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can depart anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Luffy gets here,\Nwe can set sail right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, simply put, there are about as\Nmany battleships as there are of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we could set sail, it's virtually\Nimpossible to get through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a report from the\Nfront gate in the northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed retrieval of\NEnies Lobby's marines and officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, at the front gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we identified about fifty pirates,\Nincluding the giants, escaping the main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zambai and the others!\NSee, I told you! They escaped the island okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worried about them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, they wouldn't die\Neven if you killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have finished eliminating them\Nwith a barrage of cannon fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the circumstances, no one could\Npossibly survive on the main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the number of survivors on\NEnies Lobby's main island is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a report from Battleship 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The courthouse and the Tower of Law\Nin the southeast of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as the underground passage\Nconnected to the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have all been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:19:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only target left to attack\Nis the Bridge of Hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you guys go straight to\Nthe courthouse and join Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna split into two\Nand bring the drawbridge down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La's shipwrights, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see... those guys, tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You guys're fired."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oimo... Kashii...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...deceive us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Yokozuna was with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit... Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom and Gomorrah, too...! They all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, "I'll be faithful to\NBig Bro Franky for the rest of my life!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His pectoral muscle got hurt by a trench mortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over now before he falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna be saved\Nunless you guys move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for people to die so easily like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see people on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just erase a small island from the\Nworld map, without a shred of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:21:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Buster Call is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! We came to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are waiting for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I bring you down, I won't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna try to use up\Nall your power and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred Captains\Nfrom Navy Headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many strong guys\Ndo they have to send in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That proves just how scared they are of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Hold strong until Luffy comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all make it through this\Nand leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wait for Luffy! Mortal Combat\Non the Bridge of Hesitation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
